From f42ccfa5829c3f5a18256c7474628ecbc127220a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Wiebe Cazemier <wiebe@ytec.nl>
Date: Fri, 25 Aug 2023 10:36:11 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Use vncpassword.txt for authentication

If it doesn't exist or is empty or empty-ish: it approves logins.

Logins from the loopback are also approved, for the local Venus services.

If the file becomes unreadable at some point, because of permissions for
instance, it will give an error and deny access.
